title: TikTok users flood Congress with calls as House weighs potential ban
description: TikTok users inundated congressional offices with calls on Thursday after the company urged people to “speak up” against a House measure that could ban the app.

title: Democrats probe Musk’s SpaceX, examining Russia’s alleged Starlink use
description: The lawmakers warned SpaceX that Russia’s alleged use of Starlink “poses a serious threat to Ukraine’s security, Ukrainian lives, and U.S. national security.”

title: Big Tech howled over E.U. antitrust law. The White House declined a rescue.
description: The E.U. Digital Markets Act has come into effect, forcing six major tech companies to make significant changes. The Biden administration has taken a muted approach.

title: The E.U. Digital Markets Act is here. Here’s what it means for you.
description: Alphabet, Apple, Meta and other Big Tech companies must comply with Europe’s Digital Markets Act. Here are the biggest changes users will start to see in Europe.
